net.cloud.gfx.constants

Class KeyConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.cloud.gfx.constants.KeyConstants

  • public class KeyConstants
extends java.lang.Object
    A utility class that deals with keys and their events. For example, keys for global hotkeys are stored here. There are also some custom re-purposed characters defined here. These are characters that could be typed, but are very unlikely to be useful in this application. So keys that normally do not have a character can be assigned to a character for homogeneous handling.
